channel.title: Buying Problem
channel.description:
Running Proj Fatality w/ Client 562
When im making a new shop Ex. case 4300: c.getShops().openShop(19); break;
I can open the shop, can see howmuch the buyable item is worth in the shop: .... is worth .... coins. (....million)
Everythings right. Except... Cant buy it.
They say its the number 19
c.getShops().openShop(19);
But its doing it with all the numbers 19 +/+ 99
Any Suggestions?
